title: No threat, but UK royal wedding fans in Windsor face tight security
text:
No threat, but UK royal wedding fans in Windsor face tight security 8:15am BST - 01:10
Security preparations are under way in England ahead of the royal wedding, despite there being no 'particular threat' on the day according to the wedding's tactical commander. Rough cut
